ARRANGEMENT OVER THE REQUISITE SERVICE PERIOD. EITF ISSUE NO. 06-2 IS EFFECTIVE FOR US BEGINNING JULY 1, 2007. THE CUMULATIVE EFFECT OF THE APPLICATION OF

