REDUCTION RESULTING FROM VARIOUS CHANGES IN TAX POSITIONS TAKEN IN PRIOR PERIODS, RELATED PRIMARILY TO FAVORABLE DEVELOPMENTS IN AN IRS POSITION AND MULTIPLE FOREIGN AUDIT ASSESSMENTS. THE 2006 OTHER RECONCILING ITEM INCLUDES THE IMPACT OF THE $351

