ADDITIONAL AWARDS TO PARTICIPANTS BASED ON INDIVIDUAL PERFORMANCE. ONE-QUARTER OF THE SHARES OF STOCK SUBJECT TO EACH AWARD WILL VEST FOLLOWING THE END OF THE

PERFORMANCE PERIOD, AND AN ADDITIONAL ONE-QUARTER OF THE SHARES WILL VEST OVER EACH OF THE FOLLOWING THREE YEARS.

